title: Did Biden Post Pictures of His Dogs Biting a Trump Chew Toy?
subtitle: Right-leaning observers responded with outrage at photographs of Champ and Major.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: In December 2020, President-elect Joe Biden, or an official social media account for his dogs Champ and Major, posted pictures of the dogs biting and playing with a "Donald Trump" chew toy.
